snippet: The body of a 19-year-old woman was found hanging from a eucalyptus tree, the third similar discovery in the state of Uttar Pradesh in two weeks.
abstract: Body of 19-year-old woman is found hanging from eucalyptus tree in Indian village of Uttar Pradesh; hanging is third similar discovery in state in two weeks; relatives file report alleging woman was raped and murdered by two men they say have been bothering her.
lead_paragraph: The body of a 19-year-old woman was found hanging from a eucalyptus tree, the third similar discovery in the state of Uttar Pradesh in two weeks.

headline.main: Woman Is Found Hanged in Indian State
headline.print_headline: Another Case of Hanging in Indian State
